20:25.967 --> 20:28.284
♪<i> Come on, get up</i> ♪

20:28.377 --> 20:30.544
♪<i> Just get on down</i> ♪

20:30.638 --> 20:32.379
♪<i> Just turn it up</i> ♪

20:32.398 --> 20:35.291
♪<i> Playing around, get on down</i> ♪

20:35.384 --> 20:39.737
♪<i> Yeah, it's your own time,</i>
<i> baby</i> ♪

20:39.888 --> 20:41.981
♪<i> Shoulder the pain</i> ♪

